# monday.com Knowledge for Cursor

## Entity Model

monday.com hierarchy: Account → Workspaces → Boards → Groups → Items

- **Board** = table (columns define schema, items are rows)
- **Groups** = row sections (stages like To Do / In Progress / Done)
- **Items** = records (name + column values)
- **Updates** = comments on items

## API

- Endpoint: `POST https://api.monday.com/v2` (GraphQL)
- Auth: `Authorization: <TOKEN>` header
- Version: `API-Version: 2024-10`
- Rate limit: 5M complexity points/min
- Pagination: cursor-based (`items_page` → `next_items_page`)

## Column Value JSON Formats

When setting column values via `column_values` parameter:

```
Status:     { "label": "Done" }  or  { "index": 1 }
Text:       "plain string"
Numbers:    42
